title: Did Kayleigh McEnany Tweet That Obama’s Brother Was ‘Still In That Hut In Kenya’?
subtitle: The tweet was a contribution to the hashtag #ObamaTVShows.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Former White House Press Secretary Kayleigh McEnany once tweeted: "How I Met Your Brother -- Never mind, forgot he's still in that hut in Kenya #ObamaTVShow."
